#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/writing-extensions.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Configuration objects with phase `RUNTIME` or `BUILD_AND_RUNTIME_FIXED` can be injected into recorders via constructor\n"
